    <li>End-to-end ingestion pipeline with idempotent re-indexing.</li>
    <li>Embedding model benchmarking on three domains.</li>
    <li>Hybrid search tuning — when to weight vector vs keyword.</li>
    <li>Multi-tenant index design patterns.</li>
    <li>Performance optimization: chunking, batch sizes, endpoint sizing.</li>
    <li>Cost model with three traffic-tier examples.</li>
    <li>Migration paths from external vector stores (Pinecone, Weaviate, pgvector).</li>
  </ul>

